In the absence of vaccination, the virus continues its spread within the affected countries and beyond, now adding Croatia (most probably by the same virus strain) to the list of affected countries. It will be interesting to note when this event winds down with seasonal lowering temperatures and whether it proceeds on its march during the 2015 season. - Mod.AS/CRD

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=2920414,87.]
